"12 ounces fresh Mexican chorizo*, casings removed","  About 1 tbsp. extra-virgin olive oil","1  medium onion, halved and thinly sliced","1  red bell pepper, cut into 2-in. strips","1  can (15 oz.) lima or butter beans, drained and rinsed","3  large eggs","  Salt and pepper","1  bunch cilantro with leaves and tender stems, chopped (about 2 cups)","1/2 cup crumbled queso fresco or other mild white cheese","8  corn tortillas, warmed*","  Bottled hot sauce"